column4: <content>Bird Nester. See Seb. Brant, Narrenschiff (1ste edition Basel 1494). Herre Nestrauber-Narr. The woodcut by Dürer shows a man with a fool's cap falling from a tree with a nest (or bird?) in his left hand and many dead (?) [sic] birds on the ground. The text is [...] Repr. p. 111 in F. WINKLER, Dürer und die Illustrationen zum Narrenschiff, Berlin 1951, p. 11 (as by Dürer)(adest).</content>
